---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Frenzy Photobooth | Denver's Premier Photo Booth Experience
description: Frenzy Photobooth brings the fun to your Denver events. Weddings, parties, corporate events and more. Get your photo booth quote today!
pageClass: page-home
scripts:
  - /js/lib/slider.js
  - /js/lib/config-utils.js
  - /js/lib/youtube-utils.js
  - /js/lib/media-utils.js
  - /js/features/home-video.js
  - /js/features/ui/theme.js
  - /js/features/ui/navbar-scroll.js
  - /js/features/ui/mobile-menu.js
  - /js/features/ui.js
  - /js/features/animations/counters.js
  - /js/features/animations/scroll-reveal.js
  - /js/features/animations/particles.js
  - /js/features/animations/smooth-scroll.js
  - /js/features/animations.js
  - /js/features/testimonials.js
  - /js/features/gallery/shared.js
  - /js/features/gallery/desktop.js
  - /js/features/gallery/mobile.js
  - /js/features/gallery.js
  - /js/features/theme-preview.js
  - /js/core/main.js
---
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="hero-particles" id="particles"></div>
    <div class="home-video-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
      <video id="homeVideo" class="home-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata" poster="logo.png"></video>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tagline">Denver's Premier Photo Booth Experience</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Make Every Moment <span class="gradient-text">Unforgettable</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Capture the fun, the laughter, and the memories. Frenzy Photobooth brings the party to weddings, corporate events, birthdays, and everything in between.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="{{ '/get-quote' | withBase(site.basePath) }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get a Quote</a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Our Packages</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-indicator">
      <span>Scroll</span>
      <div class="scroll-arrow"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="section about" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-images">
          <div class="about-img-wrapper img-1">
            <img src="assets/posters/event-01.jpg" alt="Guests enjoying Frenzy Photobooth" width="4000" height="6000" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          </div>
          <div class="about-img-wrapper img-2">
            <img src="assets/posters/event-02.jpg" alt="Event celebration with photobooth moments" width="4000" height="6000" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
          <p class="section-tag">About Us</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">We Bring the <span class="gradient-text">Energy</span></h2>
          <p>At Frenzy Photobooth, we believe every event deserves a splash of excitement. Based right here in Denver, Colorado, we've been turning ordinary gatherings into extraordinary memories.</p>
          <p>Our state-of-the-art photo booths come equipped with professional lighting, high-quality cameras, and an endless supply of hilarious props. Whether it's a wedding reception, a corporate gala, or a backyard birthday bash, we bring the energy that gets everyone off their seats.</p>
          <div class="about-features">
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
              <div>
                <h4>Instant Prints</h4>
                <p>High-quality prints in seconds</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="feature-icon">🎭</div>
              <div>
                <h4>Premium Props</h4>
                <p>Curated collection for every theme</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
              <div>
                <h4>Digital Sharing</h4>
                <p>Instant social media sharing</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="feature-icon">🎨</div>
              <div>
                <h4>Custom Designs</h4>
                <p>Branded overlays & templates</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Section -->
  <section class="section services" id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
